roundList.message: When you're playing on Easy, you'll earn Red stars!
Playing in Normal mode earns you both GREEN stars and RED stars.
Danger! Hard mode is only for the best of the best. Think you're ready? Give it a shot!
Playing in Hard mode earns you both GOLD stars and RED stars.
Brace yourself. The party is getting started!
Your life goes up with points but goes down with mistakes. Don't let it run out!
It's all about the timing. Hit the targets right after they change color!
Avoid making mistakes to build up your multiplier and your score!
Congratulations! You are now ready to party!
Targets are falling from the sky! Hit them when they are over the circles.
